snippet.title: INALIENABLE | He Survived the Accident, But Something Came With Him | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A man struggling with loss begins to notice something is wrong.
What’s inside him may not be entirely his own.

Still carrying guilt from a tragic accident that took his family, Eric Norris tries to move forward with his life. When strange changes begin to surface, he learns his body is host to an otherworldly presence — one that is deeply connected to him. As the truth unfolds, Eric is forced to question his identity and what it means to survive.

Director: Robert Dyke
Cast: Richard Hatch, Alan Ruck, Erick Avari.
